The '''Tarrack''' were the colonists of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Utharis]].<ref name="The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia">{{CSWECite|III|284&ndash;285|Utharis}}.</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The Tarrack feature in the novel ''[[Shield of Lies]]''. They are also mentioned in ''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''. Neither source reveals whether the term ''Tarrack'' refers to a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] or some other social group.

